name: Wsdler
body:
Wsdler
======

WSDL Parser extension for Burp

How to Run

```bash
java -classpath Wsdler.jar;burp.jar burp.StartBurp
````

Blog detailng how to use the Wsdler Plugin:

http://www.netspi.com/blog/2013/03/05/hacking-web-services-with-burp/
